    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade E46 M3 featuring the high-strung S54B32 inline-six engine and a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. This example is mechanically pristine, boasting a fully addressed VANOS system and a reinforced rear subframe to ensure chassis integrity under high lateral loads. The naturally aspirated power plant breathes through factory individual throttle bodies, delivering linear torque to the M-Variable Differential Lock. Finished in original paint with an interior devoid of typical Nappa leather bolster wear, this vehicle represents a turn-key opportunity for the enthusiast seeking peak analog performance and mechanical perfection.",
