    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Presenting an absolutely flawless 2019 Audi S5 Prestige in Navarra Blue Metallic. This vehicle has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled garage and presents as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is in pristine condition, showing a deep, mirror-like finish with zero rock chips, swirl marks, or scratches, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating and front-end paint protection film. The 19-inch Cavo design wheels are immaculate, with no curb rash, and are fitted with nearly new Michelin Pilot Sport 4S tires. Inside, the Magma Red Fine Nappa leather interior is breathtaking; the seats show no signs of wear, the bolsters are firm, and the cabin still retains its factory-fresh scent. Every feature, including the Audi Virtual Cockpit, Head-Up Display, and the 19-speaker Bang & Olufsen 3D sound system, operates with precision. Mechanically, this S5 is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history performed exclusively by Audi master technicians. There are no leaks, no squeaks, and the engine bay is clean enough to eat off of. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade example of a modern performance icon.",
      "price": 46500.0,
