      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this meticulously preserved vehicle, currently maintained in superlative condition. This specimen exhibits an uncompromising standard of care, featuring a flawless exterior finish and an interior that retains its original showroom integrity. Designed for the discerning buyer who demands mechanical excellence and aesthetic perfection, this vehicle represents a rare acquisition opportunity in today\u2019s market.",
