    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. At its heart is the S54 3.2L straight-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure VANOS system\u2014both of which have been meticulously serviced to ensure optimal cam timing and throttle response. The chassis is structurally reinforced at the subframe mounting points, a critical upgrade for this platform. Power is delivered through a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock, providing exceptional mechanical grip. The suspension geometry remains factory-spec but has been refreshed with polyurethane bushings and OEM dampers for a tight, communicative ride. This specimen is free of rod bearing concerns and retains its original factory finish, presenting an investment-grade opportunity for the true driving enthusiast.",
